snippet: Russia's anti-doping agency RUSADA said on Wednesday that comments made by its director general about sports doping had been distorted and taken out of context, the TASS news agency reported....
lead_paragraph: Russia's anti-doping agency RUSADA said on Wednesday that comments made by its director general about sports doping had been distorted and taken out of context, the TASS news agency reported.

headline.main: Russia's Anti-Doping Body Says Its Words Have Been Distorted: TASS
headline.print_headline: Russia's Anti-Doping Body Says Its Words Have Been Distorted: TASS
